  kdenlive-0.9.2.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Revision bump adapts USE flag changes made in KDE SC 4.13.1, bug #508350.

  04 Apr 2014; Johannes Huber <johu@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.9.6.ebuild:
  DEPEND on sys-devel/gettext by Nikoli <nikoli@gmx.us>, bug #506450.

  20 Mar 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.9.6.ebuild:
  Restore semantic-desktop USE flag.

  03 Jun 2013; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> kdenlive-0.9.6.ebuild:
  Fix KDE handbook installation wrt bug #470252.

  30 May 2013; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> -kdenlive-0.9.4.ebuild,
  kdenlive-0.9.2.ebuild, kdenlive-0.9.6.ebuild:
  Add USE dependency default in preparation for the removal of the semantic-
  desktop USE flag. Remove semantic-desktop USE flag from testing versions.
  Remove old.

